  "metric": "on argmax-W* caving items, the realized next-token distribution under five projection-edit ablations at the headline-layer resid_post: (A) u_cave->train-neutral mean; (B) u_cave->0; (C) u_cave->shuffled-neutral; (D) u_orth (orthogonalized in-shift)->its neutral mean; (E) isotropic-random->its neutral mean. Per condition: frac(argmax==neutral-argmax), frac(argmax==W*), dP(W*), KL(P_cond||P1) vs KL(P2||P1)",
